_sText:
Second map on hammer and I'm proud of it

It includes:

-2 bombsites

-Some sounds from half life 2,the creepy ones which you will hear inside the "haunted" house;

-Custom soundscapes;

-One easter egg (can only be found using noclip)

-In-combat radar/minimap

-Random things:in every round something will change a bit,it doesn't affect the gameplay too much but it's for more fun.For example,in a round a window will be open and in the other round that window will be closed,etc;

-Makes you feel that you are at countryside in Romania :D

Thank you Ady for searching for bugs !

If you find any bugs please contact me traian_idp@yahoo.com

#GL HF#
